# Copy to `.env` or `.env.production` before `npm run build`.
#
# Static assets base when hosted behind nginx subpath (Vite `base`).
# Example: deploy at https://example.com/reviewer/
# VITE_BASE_PATH=/reviewer
#
# API prefix when backend is not at site root. Leave empty if nginx exposes
# /health and /api at the domain root (common).
# Example: API at https://example.com/reviewer/api/ → set VITE_API_BASE=/reviewer
# VITE_API_BASE=
